Class SimpleJavaBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • gram.SimpleJavaBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SimpleJavaListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JToJListener, JToPlantListener

    public class SimpleJavaBaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements SimpleJavaListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of SimpleJavaListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
